INT. CAFÉ PARISIEN - MORNING

RENÉE sips her café au lait, reading a newspaper — the headline in bold: "MARCHÉ EN CRISE."

RENÉE
(in French, subtitled)
Ça alors... c'est incroyable.

A WAITER approaches, tray balanced with practiced ease.

WAITER
Autre chose, madame?

RENÉE
Non, merci — juste l'addition, s'il vous plaît.

The check arrives: "12,50 €."

She leaves a few coins — clink, clink — and rises to leave.

Ellipsis test... em dash test — and "curly quotes" too.
